Abstract:
    This coverage represents the townships in Iowa that have atrazine restrictions

    restrictions of 1.5 lbs./acre. 
Purpose:
    This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out acency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources.
